                        <h1>30 Days of Innovation</h1>                                  
                        <div class="page_header_block">
    <h2>Countdown to CES</h2>
    The International CES is&nbsp;about innovation.&nbsp;The most important technologies launched at <A href="http://www.CESweb.org">CES</A>, including the VCR, DVD player, HDTVand satellite radio.&nbsp;Why does the average U.S. household have 24 consumer electronics (CE) products?&nbsp; Because&nbsp;they&nbsp;improve our lives, and in times like these, making life good – especially in our homes – is more important than ever.<BR><BR>That's why this year&nbsp;we launched "30 Days of Innovation:&nbsp;The Countdown to CES," a window into the kind of technological innovation only found at <A href="http://www.CESweb.org">CES</A>. See&nbsp;30 new CES exhibitors – a new one each day – from among more than 300 companies&nbsp;showing their innovation to CES attendees for the first time.&nbsp;But this is just the beginning. Imagine learning about&nbsp;next-gen&nbsp;technology from <A href="/print/exhibitorDirectory/default.asp">2,700 of the world’s leading companies</A>&nbsp;in one trip.
