<div class="sponsorshipTitle">Day 22</div>

<STRONG>Ectaco, Inc.’s iTRAVL: Communicating in a Foreign Language Just Got Easy</STRONG><BR><IMG height=209 hspace=8 src="/print/images/photos/Ectaco_-_iTravel.gif" width=127 align=right vspace=5>Parlez vous francais?&nbsp;Communicating in a foreign language has never been so easy with <A href="http://myces.bdmetrics.com/CDT-5313804/Ectaco-Inc-/Details.aspx" target=_blank>Ectaco</A>’s iTRAVL talking 2-way multilingual language communicator and electronic dictionary.&nbsp;This handheld, voice-activated device provides unique international communications solutions.&nbsp;Whether you are at the airport, dealing with foreign partners, or visiting a doctor or restaurant, iTRAVL lets you communicate clearly and understand what is being said to you.&nbsp; The device contains everything you need to start speaking another language fluently.&nbsp;It allows you to speak directly into the device and will then provide you with an audio translation in whatever language you have selected.&nbsp; It is the must-have device for all those who love to travel, those doing business overseas or for those learning to speak another language, as it is loaded with tons of features designed to be fun, helpful and educational.<BR><BR>Check out <A href="http://myces.bdmetrics.com/CDT-5313804/Ectaco-Inc-/Details.aspx" target=_blank>Ectaco</A>’s exhibit at the Sands, Booth #73422<BR>

