<a name="2719"></a>

<div class="sponsorshipTitle">Day 23</div>

<STRONG>Black Box Innovations: Secure Your Records</STRONG><BR><IMG height=172 hspace=8 src="/print/images/photos/Black_Box_-_Pocket_Safe.jpg" width=200 align=right vspace=5><A href="http://myces.bdmetrics.com/CDT-5314836/Black-Box-Innovations/Details.aspx" target=_blank>Black Box Innovations</A> is making its CES debut with the t&acirc;ke product line. Its Personal Pocket Safe, a 2009 Innovations honoree, is a highly secure device that connects to your computer through a USB port. All data is encrypted with 256-bit AES hardware encryption and can only be accessed by entering your customizable PIN on the Pocket Safe. Once unlocked, Pocket Safe software launches and provides pre-formatted fields for easy entry of all important records and files. And the best part? There is no configuration and no software installation needed, so it can be used anywhere, and won’t leave a trace of the data on the computer being used.<BR><BR><IMG height=159 hspace=8 src="/print/images/photos/Black_Box_-_Secret_Diary.jpg" width=200 align=left vspace=5>And for consumers who crave a device for personal creativity, but with absolute security, the t&acirc;ke Secret Diary is the perfect solution. With no software installation and configuration needed, the Secret Diary is not only easy to use, but allows consumers to write, doodle and paste pictures anywhere on their secure diary page. <BR><BR><A href="http://myces.bdmetrics.com/CDT-5314836/Black-Box-Innovations/Details.aspx" target=_blank>Black Box Innovations</A> is a cutting-edge technology company, providing consumers with innovative and secure devices.&nbsp; Visit Black Box Innovations at the Sands, Booth # 72857.

