<a name="2711"></a>

<div class="sponsorshipTitle">Day 25</div>

<STRONG>Alert GPS from GPS Prevent: No More Road Worries<BR></STRONG><IMG height=180 hspace=8 src="/print/images/photos/GPSPrevent.jpg" width=206 align=right vspace=5>Never worry again while driving. <A href="http://myces.bdmetrics.com/CDT-5735630/GPS-Prevent/Details.aspx" target=_blank>GPS Prevent</A> from France is showcasing its latest in-vehicle technology, the AlerteGPS. It features a European database that notifies drivers when they are nearing fixed, mobile speed, cameras, red light cameras and danger zones. <BR><BR>This GPS-based&nbsp; detection system is a co-pilot that will help you to improve your safety and your serenity on the road. Visit <A href="http://myces.bdmetrics.com/CDT-5735630/GPS-Prevent/Details.aspx" target=_blank>GPS Prevent</A> in the LVCC North Hall, Booth #2040 at the 2009 International CES.

