<a name="2710"></a>

<div class="sponsorshipTitle">Day 26</div>

<STRONG>Powermat: Place Your Device On the Mat and Watch it Charge</STRONG><BR><IMG height=228 hspace=8 src="/print/images/photos/Powermat.gif" width=300 align=right vspace=5>The future of wireless power will be at the 2009 International CES! Our Day 27 featured exhibitor, <A href="http://myces.bdmetrics.com/CDT-5676315/Powermat/Details.aspx" target=_blank>Powermat</A> will be on hand with their latest technology that eliminates the need for wires for charging all of your favorite CE devices. Place your enabled device on the Powermat and watch it charge! Powermat is proud to offer a safer, simpler and greener alternative to overloading outlets with multiple chargers. <BR><BR><A href="http://myces.bdmetrics.com/CDT-5676315/Powermat/Details.aspx" target=_blank>Powermat</A> technology is available to a variety of surfaces including tables, floors, desktops and even walls. The most innovative part about this technology is that it has the power to transform large work surfaces and wall areas into safe and efficient conductors of electricity and is easily integrated into building construction and furniture design. You can find <A href="http://myces.bdmetrics.com/CDT-5676315/Powermat/Details.aspx" target=_blank>Powermat</A> at the 2009 International CES in the LVCC, Central Hall, Booth #12838.

